item.description: This is a joint meetup, and the game I usually go to, because it is the 1st home game of the preseason and most of the starters, including Brady, will play the entire first half. I bought the 4 tickets the morning they went on sale through Ticketmaster and these are primo seats! Section 111 Row 16 Seats 5-8 on the Patriots 50-yard line! Game starts at 730pm. We are gonna have a blast!
item.how_to_find_us: Meet at my car - Blue Mercury Sable - Parking lot of End Zone Motel on Rt 1 1/4 mile from the stadium
item.name: Patriots/Bengals Pre-Season Game
